::Prowl::

Prowl looks from Arcangle, on his shoulder, to Feline, at the table. He 
frowns as Feline shudders. There was obvioustly something he didn't know 
here...

"If you can call this a party," Prowl says to Arcangel, looking at Feline. 
"Is something wrong?" he asks her.
